quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  55,46,"Oo kan isaga ka cabsada hor istaagga Rabbigi, waxaa uu mudan labo beerood"
  55,47,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,48,Oo leh noocyo kala duwan oo badan
  55,49,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,50,Dhexdooda waxaa ah labo ilood oo dur dur ah
  55,51,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,52,Waxaaa ku yaal midho walba oo mid kastaa lammaane tahay
  55,53,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,54,"Iyagoo ku jiqlaynaya firaashyo cudbi-goodu xariir yahay, oo midhaha labadaa beerood waxay ahaan kuwo goosi dhow"
  55,55,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,56,Waxaa jooga kuwaa soo laaba araggooda ka hor iyaga aanu taaban insi iyo jin midkoodna
  55,57,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,58,La moodo dheeman iyo luul
  55,59,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,60,Miyey tahay abaalgudka samaanta wax kale aan ahayn samaan
  55,61,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,62,"Oo barbarkooda labadatani, waxaa ah labo beerood oo kale"
  55,63,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,64,Labaduba u janjeera madow cagaaran
  55,65,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,66,Dhexdooda waxaa ah labo ilood oo burqanaya
  55,67,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,68,"Waxaa dhexdooda ah midho, geedo timir iyo Rummaan"
  55,69,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,70,Waxaa dhexdooda ah khayraat iyo qurux badnooyin
  55,71,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,72,Xuurulceyn ku kooban oo aan ka bixin khaymadahooda
  55,73,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,74,Oo ka hore iyaga aanu taaban insi iyo jin midkoodna
  55,75,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,76,Iyagoo ku jiqleynaya barkimooyin cagaaran iyo gogollo qurux badan
  55,77,Ee tee baad Nicmooyinka Rabbigiin beenineysaan
  55,78,"Waxaa khayr iyo barako badan Magaca Rabbigaa, Weynaha, Sharafta Badan"